From 4db0a68676b3e4223b81b4e8b0fe383f8c68d46f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gianni Spadoni <me@gio.blue>
Date: Thu, 22 Jan 2026 20:08:44 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 03/20] arm64: dts: qcom: Enable PCIe and QCE on Ayn Odin 3

Enables PCIe and QCE

Requires patch `https://marc.info/?l=linux-kernel&m=176701225207259` for cryptobam to work

Indentation around regulators has been changed, and LDO12 and LDO15 are now always on

Signed-off-by: Gianni Spadoni <me@gio.blue>
